<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-03-15T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-03-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="617" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d617">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Marquis <persName type="from">Rudini</persName> to
                                Baron <persName type="to">Fava</persName></hi>.</head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Rome</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-03-15"><hi rend="italic">March 15,
                                1891</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>I confirm my telegram. I do not doubt that you have obtained immediately
                            energetic measures. If the slightest agitation takes place, you are
                            authorized to present a formal protest, with the reserve of asking later
                            the satisfaction to which we are entitled.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Rudini</hi>.</signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>